@nb_covid_info Those At Education have championed Bloom’s Taxonomy, including here in this 2016 document.

Perhaps Month 24 could have benefitted from some more evaluating &amp; analyzing, instead of relying on remembering how things had worked in less trying times.

https://t.co/D4lX5eAld6 https://t.co/an3mhVOEp5

@nb_covid_info Two issues I see:

1) They are claiming expertise in Covid mitigation here, but in other matters (e.g. ending masks), they are claiming they have no expertise &amp; defer to PH.

2) Whatever the source of the two years of experience, wasn’t month 24 of 24 by FAR the worst one yet? 🤔
